thread.title: Courtney

author: Courtney
title: Courtney
text: I used this to sell back my text books that I had saved until I graduated to make sure I didn't need them any more. I didn't get near as much as what I paid for them but I still would highly recommmened this company. I mean you never get what you pay for the books back and considering some were probably out dated versions I was just happy they paid me anything for them.
